{"word":"G1405 - δράσσομαι - drássomai - dras'-som-ahee - Take","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δράσσομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">drássomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dras'-som-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Take</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிடி"},{"paragraph":"to grasp with the hand, to take"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Perhaps akin to the base of <a href=\"#/G1404 - δράκων - drákōn - drak'-own/1404\">G1404</a> (through the idea of <i>capturing</i>); to <i>grasp</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>entrap:</i> - take.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}